metadata.title: TINRO - Biological Oceanographic Profile Data - Russia
metadata.description:
Irregular sampling (see TINRO Catalogue for details)

Geographic Area
NW Pacific, NE Pacific, Sea of Japan, Sea of Okhotsk, Bering Sea

Publication
Catalogue of fishery, biological and hydrological data (1980-1992) published by TINRO Regional data Center in 1995 (available from TINRO or PICES Secretariat). Additional catalogue reports frequency of observations by month and year for standard sections for the period 1952-1992

Other Comments
Data from 1981-1995 is available (in Russia) in electronic form; older data exists in paper record in TINRO archive

A TCODE project
